#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16588
msgid "Setting up desktop environment"
msgstr "Configurer l'environnement de bureau"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16589
msgid "A <ulink url=\"&desktopenvironment;\">desktop environment</ulink> is usually a combination of a <ulink url=\"&xwindowmanager;\">X window manager</ulink>, a file manager, and a suite of compatible utility programs."
msgstr "Un <ulink url=\"&desktopenvironment;\">environnement de bureau</ulink> est habituellement constitué de la combinaison d'un <ulink url=\"&xwindowmanager;\">gestionnaire X Window</ulink>, d'un gestionnaire de fichiers et d'une suite compatible de programmes utilitaires."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16590
msgid "You can setup a full <ulink url=\"&desktopenvironment;\">desktop environment</ulink> such as <ulink url=\"&gnome;\">GNOME</ulink>, <ulink url=\"&kde;\">KDE</ulink>, <ulink url=\"&xfce;\">Xfce</ulink>, or <ulink url=\"&lxde;\">LXDE</ulink>, from the <literal>aptitude</literal> under the task menu."
msgstr "Vous pouvez configurer un <ulink url=\"&desktopenvironment;\">environnement de bureau</ulink> complet tel que <ulink url=\"&gnome;\">GNOME</ulink>, <ulink url=\"&kde;\">KDE</ulink>, <ulink url=\"&xfce;\">Xfce</ulink> ou <ulink url=\"&lxde;\">LXDE</ulink> depuis le menu des tâches d'<literal>aptitude</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><tip><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16592
msgid "Task menu may be out of sync with the latest package transition state under Debian <literal>unstable</literal>/<literal>testing</literal> environment. In such situation, you need to deselect some (meta)packages listed under <literal>aptitude</literal>(8) task menu to avoid package conflicts.  When deselecting (meta)packages, you must select certain packages providing their dependencies manually to avoid them deleted automatically."
msgstr "Sous les environnements Debian <literal>unstable</literal> et <literal>testing</literal>, le menu Tâches peut être désynchronisé de l'état des dernières transitions des paquets. Dans une telle situation, vous devrez, afin d'éviter des conflits de paquets, désélectionner certains paquets ou méta-paquets du menu des tâches d'<literal>aptitude</literal>. Lors de la désélection de paquets ou de méta-paquets, vous devrez sélectionner vous-même certains paquets qui fournissent leurs dépendances afin d'éviter qu'ils ne soient automatiquement supprimés."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16594
msgid "You may alternatively setup a simple environment manually just with a <ulink url=\"&xwindowmanager;\">X window manager</ulink> such as <ulink url=\"&fluxbox;\">Fluxbox</ulink>."
msgstr "Vous pouvez aussi mettre en place manuellement un environnement simple n'ayant qu'un <ulink url=\"&xwindowmanager;\">gestionnaire X Window</ulink> comme <ulink url=\"&fluxbox;\">Fluxbox</ulink>."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16595
msgid "See <ulink url=\"&windowmanagersforx;\">Window Managers for X</ulink> for the guide to the X window manager and the desktop environment."
msgstr "Voir <ulink url=\"&windowmanagersforx;\">gestionnaires de fenêtres pour X</ulink> pour un guide du gestionnaire de fenêtres X et de l'environnement de bureau."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16597
msgid "Debian menu"
msgstr "Menu Debian"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16598
msgid "<ulink url=\"&debianmenusystem;\">Debian menu system</ulink> provides a general interface for both text- and X-oriented programs with <literal>update-menus</literal>(1) from the <literal>menu</literal> package.  Each package installs its menu data in the \"<literal>/usr/share/menu/</literal>\" directory. See \"<literal>/usr/share/menu/README</literal>\"."
msgstr "Le <ulink url=\"&debianmenusystem;\">système de menus Debian</ulink> fournit une interface aux programmes qu'ils soient en mode texte ou orientés X avec <literal>update-menus</literal>(1) du paquet <literal>menu</literal>. Chaque paquet installe ses données de menu dans le répertoire «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/menu/</literal>&nbsp;». Voir «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/menu/README</literal>&nbsp;»."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16601
msgid "Freedesktop.org menu"
msgstr "Menu de Freedesktop.org"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16602
msgid "Each package which is compliant to Freedesktop.org's xdg menu system installs its menu data provided by \"<literal>*.desktop</literal>\" under \"<literal>/usr/share/applications/</literal>\". Modern desktop environments which are compliant to Freedesktop.org standard use these data to generate their menu using the <literal>xdg-utils</literal> package.  See \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/xdg-utils/README</literal>\"."
msgstr "Chaque paquet conforme au système de menu xdg du système Freedesktop.org installe ses données de menu fournies par «&nbsp;<literal>*.desktop</literal>&nbsp;» dans «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/applications/</literal>&nbsp;». Les environnements de bureau modernes conformes au standard Freedesktop.org utilisent ces données afin de créer leur menu à l'aide du paquet <literal>xdg-utils</literal>. Voir «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/doc/xdg-utils/README</literal>&nbsp;»."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16605
msgid "Debian menu under GNOME desktop environment"
msgstr "Menu Debian avec l'environnement de bureau GNOME"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16606
msgid "In order to obtain access to the traditional Debian menu under GNOME desktop environment, you must install the <literal>menu-xdg</literal> package, click \"System\" → \"Preference\" → \"Main Menu\", and check the box for \"Debian\"."
msgstr "Afin d'accéder au menu Debian traditionnel depuis l'environnement de bureau GNOME, vous devez installer le paquet <literal>menu-xdg</literal>, cliquez«&nbsp;Système&nbsp;» → «&nbsp;Préférence&nbsp;» → «&nbsp;Menu principal&nbsp;» et cochez la case correspondant à «&nbsp;Debian&nbsp;»."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:16608
msgid "You may need to do the similar for other modern desktop environments which are compliant to Freedesktop.org standard."
msgstr "Vous pouvez faire la même chose avec d'autres environnements de bureau modernes conformes à la norme Freedesktop.org."

