# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18341
msgid "The environment variable \"<literal>LANG=xx_YY.ZZZZ</literal>\" sets the locale to language code \"<literal>xx</literal>\", country code \"<literal>yy</literal>\", and encoding \"<literal>ZZZZ</literal>\" (see <xref linkend=\"_literal_lang_literal_variable\"/>)."
msgstr "La variable d'environnement «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=xx_YY.ZZZZ</literal>&nbsp;» définit les paramètres linguistiques avec le code de langue «&nbsp;<literal>xx</literal>&nbsp;», le code de pays «&nbsp;<literal>yy</literal>&nbsp;» et le codage «&nbsp;<literal>ZZZZ</literal>&nbsp;» (voir <xref linkend=\"_literal_lang_literal_variable\"/>)."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18342
msgid "Current Debian system normally sets the locale as \"<literal>LANG=xx_YY.UTF-8</literal>\".  This uses the <ulink url=\"&utfi;\">UTF-8</ulink> encoding with the <ulink url=\"&unicode;\">Unicode</ulink> character set. This <ulink url=\"&utfi;\">UTF-8</ulink> encoding system is a multibyte code system and uses code points smartly. The <ulink url=\"&ascii;\">ASCII</ulink> data, which consist only with 7-bit range codes, are always valid UTF-8 data consisting only with 1 byte per character."
msgstr "Le système Debian actuel définit normalement les paramètres linguistiques avec «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=xx_YY.UTF-8</literal>&nbsp;». Ceci utilise le codage <ulink url=\"&utfi;\">UTF-8</ulink> avec le jeu de caractères<ulink url=\"&unicode;\">Unicode</ulink>. Ce système de codage <ulink url=\"&utfi;\">UTF-8</ulink> est un système de code multi-octets qui utilise intelligemment les éléments du code. Les données <ulink url=\"&ascii;\">ASCII</ulink>, qui sont uniquement constituées de code sur 7 bits, sont toujours des données UTF-8 valables qui ne comportent qu'un octet par caractère."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18343
msgid "Previous Debian system used to set the locale as \"<literal>LANG=C</literal>\" or \"<literal>LANG=xx_YY</literal>\" (without \"<literal>.UTF-8</literal>\")."
msgstr "Le système Debian précédent définissait habituellement les paramètres linguistiques avec «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=C</literal>&nbsp;» ou «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=xx_YY</literal>&nbsp;» (sans «&nbsp;<literal>.UTF-8</literal>&nbsp;»)."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18347
msgid "The <ulink url=\"&ascii;\">ASCII</ulink> character set is used for \"<literal>LANG=C</literal>\" or \"<literal>LANG=POSIX</literal>\"."
msgstr "Le jeu de caractères <ulink url=\"&ascii;\">ASCII</ulink> est utilisé avec «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=C</literal>&nbsp;» ou «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=POSIX</literal>&nbsp;»."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18352
msgid "The traditional encoding system in Unix is used for \"<literal>LANG=xx_YY</literal>\"."
msgstr "Le système de codage traditionnel sous Unix est utilisé pour «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=xx_YY</literal>&nbsp;»."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:18356
msgid "Actual traditional encoding system used for \"<literal>LANG=xx_YY</literal>\" can be identified by checking \"<literal>/usr/share/i18n/SUPPORTED</literal>\".  For example, \"<literal>en_US</literal>\" uses \"<literal>ISO-8859-1</literal>\" encoding and \"<literal>fr_FR@euro</literal>\" uses \"<literal>ISO-8859-15</literal>\" encoding."
msgstr "Le système de codage traditionnel actuel utilisé pour «&nbsp;<literal>LANG=xx_YY</literal>&nbsp;» peut être identifié en vérifiant «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/i18n/SUPPORTED</literal>&nbsp;». Par exemple, «&nbsp;<literal>en_US</literal>&nbsp;» utilise le codage «&nbsp;<literal>ISO-8859-1</literal>&nbsp;» et «&nbsp;<literal>fr_FR@euro</literal>&nbsp;» utilise le codage «&nbsp;<literal>ISO-8859-15</literal>."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
