msgstr "<ulink url=\"&atutorialintroductiontogit;\">Un tutoriel d'introduction à git</ulink> «&nbsp;A tutorial introduction to git&nbsp;» (<literal>/usr/share/doc/git-doc/gittutorial.html</literal>)"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
