msgstr "«&nbsp;<literal>http://www.foo.dom/programme.php?VAR1=VAL1&amp;VAR2=VAL2&amp;VAR3=VAL3</literal>&nbsp;»"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:30867
